<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="170" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,788,887]" pageId="5" pageNumber="170">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,788,815]" pageId="5" pageNumber="170">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Two pairs of orbital setae. Arista short, shorter than width of head in lateral view. No sexual dimorphism in width of postfrons and facial plate. 1 + 3 
<emphasis box="[640,666,824,850]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="170">dc</emphasis>
arising from dark spots. Vein R 
<subScript attach="left" box="[1022,1030,843,857]" fontSize="6" pageId="5" pageNumber="170">1</subScript>
joining Costa proximal to crossvein r-m.
</paragraph>
